-C%C3%B4ng-An-th%C3%A1i-d%E1%BB%8Bch-sa-m%C3%B4n/poem-y4hw-QosnW_T7qHFXEzMCA">Lưu biệt Công An thái dịch sa môn - 留別公安太易沙門</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Ph%C3%BA-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-h%E1%BB%93ng-mai-hoa-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-fbLb4cV5a4OAJeETdqz1KQ">Phú đắc hồng mai hoa kỳ 2 - 賦得紅梅花其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tu%C3%BD-ca-h%C3%A0nh-t%E1%BA%B7ng-C%C3%B4ng-An-Nhan-th%E1%BA%ADp-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7-th%E1%BB%89nh-C%E1%BB%91-b%C3%A1t-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-b%C3%ADch/poem-OmQxrd4OxiuGOfZIDuWp0A">Tuý ca hành tặng Công An Nhan thập thiếu phủ thỉnh Cố bát đề bích - 醉歌行贈公安顏十少府請顧八題壁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Vi%E1%BB%85n-du-Giang-kho%C3%A1t-ph%C3%B9-cao-%C4%91%E1%BB%91ng/poem-G0i4dJiLIOYZivh8myuVSg">Viễn du (Giang khoát phù cao đống) - 遠遊（江闊浮高凍）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
